author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Learn more about the Jazzinc 1/12 Batwing: https://jazzincdioramas.com/1-12-scale/112-scale-ultimate-1989-batwing

After our original review of the 1/6 scale Batwing replica, we check out Jazzinc Diorama's prototype of their 1/12 scale Batwing that they're developing for collectors. With newfound reference photos of the massive filming miniature use in the 1989 Batman film, we're able to see upgrades made to this model to make it even more accurate than its larger-scale predecessor. We're impressed by the quality of this prototype--just look at the details in the cockpit! 

Our review of the 1/6 scale Jazzinc Batwing: https://youtu.be/U2avwjqxa34
The original Batwing model restored: https://youtu.be/0STyxqVXaXI

Shot by Josh Self and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
